  m_text: "Welcome to the Interactive Museum\n\nHow to Use:\n\n1 - Tap the START
    button to turn on the camera\n2 - Point the camera at a product image\n3 - A
    3D model will appear on the image\n4 - Interact with the model:\n\u2022 Drag
    with one finger \u2192 Rotate\n\nAvailable Products:\n\nPrecision Scale\nLandline
    Phone\nOptical Microscope\nCamera\nGramophone\n\nTip: Make sure the lighting
    is good!"
